#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_versions/3.0/guides/command-mode-reference.adoc:262
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"@QuarkusMainTest\n"
"@TestProfile(MyTestProfile.class)\n"
"public class MyCommandModeTest {\n"
